 bullion trader in India. The company operates in two segments: Trading of Commodities and Securities and Corporate Advisory Services. It offers gold and silver bars and coins of various sizes and weights; and provides wholesale delivery of bullion to domestic users, such as ornament manufacturers, goldsmiths, jewelers, and semi-wholesalers, as well as individual customers. The company operates the Aurel Bullion App, a bullion trading platform that enables customers to buy and sell gold and silver bars and coins, as well as provides a b2b physical bullion trading solution, primarily serving jewelers, while also enabling serious individual buyers to access physical bullion directly, customized jewelry sourcing, Aurel Bullion Pro, chatgpt-powered assistant dedicated to physical bullion trading. In addition, the company provides Aurel gold purchase plans; and financial consulting and advisory services to small businesses in the fields of restructuring, compliance, and risk management. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Amritsar, India."}}